{"tid":377124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道發現女性遺體疑為失蹤福建教師","createTime":"2017-08-27T13:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T15:43:57.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52380c88d9db0d3967cb9b976a21ffec95a20bce","tid":377124,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=233824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233824&d=H2dqvVENTcqX0qiaRhYNc5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e2aa3962\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D233824&h=0fb2203d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=233824</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】日本北海道釧路市海邊發現一具女性屍體，懷疑是失蹤逾一個月的中國籍教師危秋潔。<br />\n<br />\n釧路市漁民周日清晨，發現一具年輕女性屍體被沖上岸邊，警方接報後到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方消息指，女性遺體長頭髮，身高約1.6米，身穿白色上衣，戴紅色絲巾，衣著外表跟上月底失蹤的福建教師危秋潔相似。<br />\n<br />\n遺體部分已見骨，屍身多處有損傷，相信已死去逾一個月，當局正進行DNA驗證，並調查死因。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的危秋潔，上月18日獨自到北海道旅遊，期間下落不明，她最後一次被人目擊是在上月23日於釧路市一間咖啡店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.laonanren.com/Public/pageimg/20170727/1501134006952835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.laonanren.com%2FPublic%2Fpageimg%2F20170727%2F1501134006952835.jpg&h=2700fa7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7ba45fab138f12c2dfff09d37e6115f945d8193","tid":377124,"uid":13554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"張圖係個老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5be9eaa6b1e93df0d69c4fe23d6d8dc44df8ce","tid":377124,"uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張圖係個老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<b